Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=docs:$PATH && export PS1='$ ' && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "warroom run 'Add a hello world Express server'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 28s
Sleep 3s
